      "text": "Electric Substantive Rules - Chapter 25 - 25.192 - Transmission Service Rates\n\nHome Rules and Laws Substantive Chapter 25 - Electric Transmission Service Rates\n\nNavigation\n\n- Home\n- Contact\n- PUCT En Español\n\nPublic Utility Commission\n\n- Consumer\n- Industry\n- Rules & Laws\n- Filings\n- Agency\n\nAbout the PUCT\n\n- Jobs at the PUC\n- Mission and History\n- Office of Public Engagement\n- PUCT Commissioners\n- PUCT Policies\n- Procurement Information\n\nResources\n\n- Agency Reports\n- Calendar\n- Consumer Information\n- Cybersecurity Information\n- PUCT News Releases\n- Publications\n\nRules and Laws\n\n- Administrative Rules\n- Procedural Rules\n- Participating in a PUCT Proceeding\n- Recent Rule Changes\n- Statutes\n- Substantive Rules & Laws\n- Telecom Interconnection Rules\n\nContact Us\n\n- Contact Us\n- Staff Directory\n- Department Directory\n- Directions and Map\n- Website Support\n\nMenu\n\n# Electric Substantive Rules - Chapter 25\n\n## §25.192 - Transmission Service Rates.\n\n§25.192(12/20/22)\n\nOrder Adopting Amendments to §25.192 as Approved at the November 30, 2022 Open Meeting\n\nProposal for Publication of Amendments to §25.192 as Approved at the August 4, 2022 Open Meeting\n\nOrder Adopting Amendments to §§25.101, 25.174, and 25.192 as Approved at the June 9, 2016 Open Meeting\n\nProposal for Publication of Amendments to §§25.101, 25.174, and 25.192 as Approved at the February 11, 2016 Open Meeting\n\nOrder Adopting Amendment to §25.192 and §25.501 as Approved at the March 7, 2012 Open Meeting\n\nProposal for Publication of Amendment to §25.192 and §25.501 as Approved at the December 8, 2011, Open Meeting\n\nOrder Adopting Amendment to §25.192 as Approved at the July 30, 2010 Open Meeting\n\nProposal for Publication of Amendment to §25.192 as Approved at the January 29, 2010 Open Meeting\n\nOrder\n\nOrder Adopting Amendments, New Rules and Repeals Consistent with the New Market Design Developed by ERCOT as Approved at th