      "text": "SUBJECT: CNP Files TCRF Update Effective March 1, 2026\n\nNOTICE DATE: December 1, 2025\n\nNOTICE TYPE: Initial\n\nSHORT DESCRIPTION: On December 1, 2025, CenterPoint Energy filed a TCRF (Transmission Cost Recovery Factor) update with the PUC under Docket No. 59042.\n\nINTENDED AUDIENCE: Competitive Retailers\n\nLONG DESCRIPTION: On December 1, 2025, CenterPoint Energy filed a TCRF (Transmission Cost Recovery Factor) update with the PUC under Docket No. 59042, with an effective date of March 1, 2026. The TCRF amount to be recovered on a semi-annual basis is $735.7 million, and in addition, a prior six-month over-recovery true-up adjustment of $64.7 million for a total of $671.0 million.\n\nADDITIONAL INFORMATION: Notice will be provided to the Market upon approval of this filing.\n\nCompetitive Retailer Relations CenterPoint Energy Houston Electric, LLC\n\n",
